episodes.title: How I Escaped the IFB Cult - SA Survivor - Amber Interview
episodes.description:
In this eye-opening video, Amber shares her story of growing up in the Independent Fundamental Baptist (IBF) church, and how it has shaped her life.  From the strict rules and regulations to the SA, physical, and emotional abuse. Amber will reveal the dark side of her childhood.  If you're a survivor of a cult experience or are interested in cult recovery, this video is for you. Join Amber as she opens up about her journey and shares her experiences of breaking free from the cult's grasp.
